MailFang - The Email Testing Tool You've Been Waiting For

Test your emails locally during development, deploy in a sandbox, or use in your staging environment instead of sending emails to an external service. Regain control of your data and eliminate unnecessary costs.

KEY FEATURES:

✓ Easy deployment via Docker or single file binary
✓ View rendered email content, inspect headers, attachments and raw emails
✓ Preview emails in different viewports and block remote content loading
✓ Real-time updates in the web UI
✓ Modern, intuitive interface

QUICK START:

docker run --name mailfang \
           -p 3000:3000 \
           -p 2525:2525 \
           -d cars10/mailfang

Open the web UI on http://localhost:3000 and send emails to localhost:2525.

WHY MAILFANG?

• Local Development: Test emails without external dependencies
• Data Control: Keep your email data private and secure
• Cost Effective: No per-email charges or subscription fees
• Developer Friendly: Simple configuration and deployment
• Production Ready: Use in staging environments with confidence

Get started today: https://github.com/cars10/mailfang

